<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Forest Heights</h2>
    <div>
        <p class="par-lg">A small but well-planned residential community located within the South-East Quadrant of Calgary, Forest Heights is flanked by the <a href="/forest-lawn.php">Forest Lawn</a> on the south. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">The community is also surrounded by the <a href="/penbrooke-meadows.php">Penbrooke Meadows</a> on the east, the Fonda on the west, the 17 Avenue on the south and the Memorial Drive on its northern boundary.</p>
        <p class="par-lg">Forest Heights Real Estate offers its future residents a variety of affordable housing options ranging from townhomes, single-family detached units as well as apartment condos that are typically available at an average price of $350,000. </p>
    </div>
</div>